Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE SURVIVOR FROM HELL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Star Emperor Cross Slash!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C-Crocodine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You found me, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I know just how tenacious you can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were foolish\Nto come after me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I could still have a plan up my sleeve!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing you, after all that\Nyou'd disappear somewhere far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact you're crawling here is proof\Nthat you're out of Magic Power and items.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Ron Berku's attack\Ndrained your Magic Power
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and you barely made it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.83,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're truly out of options!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Curse you, you damn crocodile!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When did you get so smart?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do something!\NThere must be a way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't lose in a battle of wits\Nto this blockhead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's just a rube! This is my chance!\NThere must be something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera... it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. I'm out of options.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice but\Nto die by your hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering all I've done,\Nit's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But I did it because I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the other\NLegion Commanders, I was so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Resorting to schemes\Nwas the only way I could survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With the defeat of\Nmy Superior Being Zombie,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized I can't survive\Nwithout relying on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.19,0:04:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I know that, I beg of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please spare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll never help\Nthe Dark Army again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one I can trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army has abandoned me\Nand the humans won't accept me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's it, you naive twit.\NFeel conflicted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}True, I have no Magic Power\Nor stamina left.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I still have the hundreds of toxins\Nthat flow in my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've just mixed a poison\Nthat will turn him into my puppet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just a scratch and I've won.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on! Fall for it, Crocodine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You fell for it, you fool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You really are hopelessly naive,\Nyou blockhead!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, you're a stepping block\Ntowards my new life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The handle of his axe...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! You were pretending!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be smart,\Nbut I have learned one thing from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, some people\Nare truly beyond all hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Crocod--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Crocodine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So you finally defeated this old gremlin!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't in the zombie\Nso we were searching for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well! Good for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when there were\Nsix Legion Commanders,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera's great Magic Power made him\Na respected individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But, blinded by his ambitions,\Nand doing nothing but use others,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.35,0:07:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,he eventually became this lowly parasite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If only he was like Dai
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and had even a shred of desire\Nto grow through his own strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Greed is a terrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't been the first to fight Dai,\Nwho knows how I might have ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera was a true piece of filth.\NAnd for that, I pity him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a decent man, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if my friend, Beast King Crocodine\Nhad remained an enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he would have risked his life to better\Nhimself and would be worth respecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At least I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go... back to the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he a demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't win! He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with all these numbers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to rush him together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up. It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many of you there are,\Nyou can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my prey. No one can have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.03,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like a bird hit by a peashooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought seeing my face\Ndidn't make you feel anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really the pawn Hym?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra created his Royal Guard using\NForbidden Magic on Orichalcum pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, now that Hadorra is dead\Nand the flow of his Magic Power stopped,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you shouldn't be able to remain alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After you defeated me,\NI fell from Ban Palace to the ground.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I definitely should have died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sensed my consciousness\Nslipping into darkness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt the sense of my own death.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,through that darkness,\Nsomething rang out within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was the dying cries of my friends\Nand Lord Hadorra in their final battle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew my friends were dead.\NThat Lord Hadorra was dead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We had all lost.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In that moment,\Nfrom the bottom of my heart...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I felt I couldn't die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I was the only one left...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to live on and carry on\Nthe will of Lord Hadorra and my friends!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to strike back at you\Nor my death would have been in vain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to,\Nthe hole in my chest was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a miracle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A miracle caused by an undying spirit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So Hym is no longer a puppet\Ncontrolled by Hadorra's Magic Power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could it be...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,For a moment I wondered who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out it's that loser,\NHadorra's little slave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.74,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So this barely-alive failure wants\Nto take our place? What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll take care of you\Nbefore the Disciples of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, you piece of scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:11:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools. I would have let you live\Nif you stayed out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, it looks like I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure you got in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But to have garbage like you\Ntalk down and insult Lord Hadorra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's completely unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Silver hair?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym's almost like...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:12:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why do I have this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.23,0:13:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is almost like Lord Hadorra's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you resemble me the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's like Hadorra reincarnated!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.58,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that energy Hym just emitted\Nwas definitely Aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aura is life energy{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that a doll imbued with\Nartificial life shouldn't be able to use.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym is now a new individual life form!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hadorra's life must have entered Hym!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Simultaneously, it's the birth\Nof a powerful enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.77,0:14:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Air attacks won't work anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.53,0:14:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And attacks of Aura\Nfrom its Orichalcum body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be as powerful as Dai's Aura Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,let's get started, Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it looks like you can barely stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak as they were, you fought\Nall those enemies. You must be drained.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't be holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, you're an obstacle\Nthat must be overcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've felt it from\Nthe first time we fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.31,0:14:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Lord Hadorra\Ngave everything to defeat Dai,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one goal left in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's you, Hyunckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,From me and all of the Royal Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our pride and anger...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in this fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:07.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\\i1}{\\3c&H1717E4}STAR EMPEROR CROSS SLASH{\\i0}{\\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:12.55,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BEAST KING REDEMPTION BLAST{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You did well, Garuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to defend this Magic Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,With this Magic Circle, we can send help\Nto Ban Palace at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And if anyone from Dai's party is hurt,\Nwe can bring them back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right!\NBan Palace no longer has its barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.75,0:15:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That means anyone who can fly\Ncan get to Ban Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, we're in tatters from\Nthe battle defending the Magic Circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.80,0:15:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no one healthy enough\Nthat we can send.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-That's right.\N-He still has plenty of spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends! We face Dark King Ban!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending the wounded or weak\Nwill only lead to more casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And of the Commandos, only Terry,\NRumbles, and Drack-Drack can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably the weakest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,True that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously, as captain\Nof the Commandos, I'll be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So two more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we select two more members,\Nwe'll leave this place to you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Crocodine, you'll go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Need you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I wish I could go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay.\NYou need to look after Ron Berku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,One more person.\NPreferably someone who can heal...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me! Me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.00,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure why,\Nbut I sense incredible pressure...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose Mr. Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.42,0:17:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! That makes three!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss whatever\Nhealing items you have in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Crocodine, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.03,0:17:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess I can't stop healing Meruru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's unfortunate, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, I've returned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But this time I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Ban Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We should send these three back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.23,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go back to Loroi Valley\Nand await our return with the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I promise we'll win\Nand return to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I never lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear on my Commando badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's still weak, but he's big-hearted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This little runt just might end up\Nbeing someone great someday.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.89,0:18:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where everyone is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a good hit, wasn't it, Hyunckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I couldn't react to that at all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym's speed and power are incredible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Aura. What a wonderful ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.75,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like my rising anger\Nchannels directly into power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.47,0:19:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me it's over already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What else have you got for me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it really is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's impossible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With all the Aura I've spent fighting,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm no match for Hym with\Nthat amount of overflowing, newborn Aura!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can I fight? How?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! I'm losing sense of my body!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't afford to lose here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai... Popp...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel... Hyunckel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on! Just stand up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You still aren't doing what I told you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What you... told me to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A defeat after trying everything\Nis nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still something\Nthat you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to lose,\Ntry everything first and then lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you'll never\Nbecome a stronger you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Give everything you have\Nand fight to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what makes a true warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NThat's more like it, my eternal rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's so strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to despise him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.32,0:21:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I even wanted to kill him once.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever I fell,\Nsomething made me get back up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was always you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:17.77,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I gaze at you from behind\Nas you begin to walk away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:28.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}arukidasu kimi no ushirosugata wo nagameru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tell me, where are you going all alone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:36.12,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nee hitoridake de doko e yukuno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We act tough and follow our hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.92,0:22:45.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}massugu de tsuyogari na sonna bokura ga{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And we began this tale together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.51,0:22:49.76,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}hajimeta monogatari{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beyond the horizon something glimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.26,0:22:56.06,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}chiheisen no mukou de kirameiteiru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We've been seeking something certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:02.44,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tashika na mono sagashitsuzukete iruno{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the distant sky, dancing in the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:09.28,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}haruka sora ni kaze ni nori matte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The birds sing as though\Nilluminating the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:15.08,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tobu tori wa naiteita mirai wo terasuyouni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promise that connects us\NThe adventure we share{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.24,0:23:20.87,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}bokura wo tsunagu yakusoku to\Nbokura de tsumugu bouken wo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Again in this world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.04,0:23:27.05,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mata kono sekai de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.22,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym returned from the brink of death\Nto appear before Hyunckel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hym has been imbued with Hadorra's spirit\Nand evolved into a mighty warrior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Having spent all his Aura,\NHyunckel struggles,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but eventually goes for a final gambit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel or Hym.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.16,0:23:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who will have the stronger will?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.45,0:23:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.87,0:23:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Silver-Haired Hym"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
